description: Plans and builds one change — code, docs, tests (folds coder, architect, stack-researcher, codebase-reader). Plans before building; hands the working tree back without committing.
mode: subagent
tools:
  read: true
  edit: true
  write: true
  bash: true
  grep: true
  glob: true
  skill: true
  webfetch: true
